WEBVTT

00:08:58.576 --> 00:09:00.410
in the capital of Laos.

00:09:01.568 --> 00:09:04.689
This was one of the lowest
points in my life.

00:09:05.571 --> 00:09:10.758
I did everything to get
my family to freedom,

00:09:10.782 --> 00:09:13.132
and we came so close,

00:09:13.156 --> 00:09:15.429
but my family was thrown in jail,

00:09:15.453 --> 00:09:18.424
just a short distance
from the South Korean embassy.

00:09:19.297 --> 00:09:22.053
I went back and forth
between the immigration office

00:09:22.077 --> 00:09:23.955
and the police station,

00:09:23.979 --> 00:09:26.892
desperately trying to get my family out.

00:09:26.916 --> 00:09:30.599
but I didn't have enough money
to pay a bribe or fine anymore.